==Powers and Abilities==
===Powers===
<!-- The power list and levels has been carefully reviewed and approved with the media released post The Marvels. DO NOT MAKE arbitrary changes to them or it may lead to blocks. If something is wrong, please contact WikiProjects: Powers & Abilities -->
{{Quote|When did you get powers?"<br>"I walked through the radiation shielding [[Westview Anomaly|barrier]] of a [[Scarlet Witch|witch]]'s hex, and now I can manipulate and see all wavelengths of the electromagnetic spectrum.|[[Carol Danvers]] and Monica Rambeau|The Marvels}}
*'''Artificially Enhanced Physiology''': [[File:Rambeau Straight Ahead.png|thumb|250px|Rambeau in binary form]] While getting shot out of the [[Hex]] by [[Wanda Maximoff]], Rambeau realized that her DNA had been altered from that and her initial descent into it. Trying to get back into the Hex, Rambeau pushed her way through and eventually came out the other side with completely changed DNA, allowing her many abilities like energy absorption and being able to see the electromagnetic fields.
**'''Superhuman Strength''': Rambeau gained superhuman strength, which allowed her to be able to punch a [[Kree]] soldier during a battle at the [[Khan Residence]]. She also fought against the all-powerful [[Dar-Benn]] and launched the Kree against the wall with her [[Universal Weapon]].
**'''Superhuman Durability''': Rambeau's resistance to bodily harm was also greatly increased, allowing her withstand a forced fall from [[Wanda Maximoff]] and also battles against the [[Kree]] at the [[Khan Residence]], on [[Aladna]] and even on an [[Accuser Warship]].
**'''Superhuman Speed''': Rambeau quickly learned that her speed had increased greatly as well, allowing her both faster running and flying. This allowed her to quickly run in front of [[Billy Maximoff|Billy]] and [[Tommy Maximoff]] to stop bullets shot by [[Tyler Hayward]].
**'''Superhuman Agility''': Rambeau also became very agile which allowed her to dodge some attacks by [[Kree]] and even bullets. She was also able to quickly block a [[Universal Weapon]] attack by [[Dar-Benn]].
**'''Superhuman Stamina''': Rambeau's stamina was enhanced after her exposure to the Hex's energy, allowing her to exert herself at peak capacity for long periods of time without tiring or showing any sign of fatigue, as shown during her fights with the [[Kree]] soldiers and [[Dar-Benn]].
**'''Superhuman Reflexes''': Rambeau is able to augment her reaction time proficiently enough to track passing bullets with her eyes. Her reflexes also allowed her to dodge many attacks, shots and blasts from [[Kree]] soldiers and [[Dar-Benn]].
**'''Electromagnetism Manipulation''': Rambeau's events with the border of the [[Hex]] notably gave her abilities revolving around the electromagnetic spectrum.
***'''Electromagnetic Vision''': [[File:Spectrum Vision.png|thumb|250px|Rambeau seeing with her spectral vision]] Very notably, Rambeau gained the ability to perceive various forms of electromagnetic energy, and was able to use this spectral vision to detect mystical energy running through [[Agatha Harkness]]'s cellar and [[Ralph Bohner]]'s [[Enchanted Necklace|necklace]]. When she first got her powers, she could also see the energy coming off of the power lines. Whenever Rambeau's powers utilize, her eyes glow with different colors around her entire iris, turning it blue. Additionally, Rambeau was able to get readings on the broken [[Jump Points|jump point]] to [[X-Men Ally Binary Universe|another universe]].
***'''Electromagnetic Absorption''': While going through the Hex, Rambeau gained the ability to absorb all forms of energy, which causes her eyes to glow blue when in use. After being attacked by [[Wanda Maximoff]], who hoisted her into the air and let her go, Rambeau used this power to absorb the impact of her fall. During the [[Battle of Westview]], she absorbed the kinetic energy of several bullets as they passed through her body, except for one, which was stopped by Billy. After joining [[S.A.B.E.R.]], Rambeau learned to redirect the energy she has absorbed against her enemies. While fighting a Kree soldier, she absorbed the energy from his weapon and used it to empower her punch. She showed this again when she absorbed an attack from Dar-Benn's [[Universal Weapon]] and shot the energy back in a photon blast. She also used this ability when she absorbed [[Kamala Khan]] and [[Carol Danvers]]' energy blasts, which activated her energy form.
***'''Electromagnetic Blast''': [[File:Dar-Benn vs Monica.png|thumb|250px|Rambeau blasts [[Dar-Benn]]]] Rambeau can fire beams of electromagnetic energy out of her hands and can even infuse that energy into her hands to deliver powerful punches, capable of knocking back Kree soldiers. However these beams can be absorbed by [[Dar-Benn]]'s [[Quantum Bands|Quantum Band]], which proved costly for the [[Marvels]]. She even used her projection to focus on a tiny part of the [[S.A.B.E.R. Space Station]] to fix it.
***'''Flight''': Rambeau had been trying to practice her flight. However, despite much worry, she was forced to use it to catch [[Kamala Khan]] who was falling out of the sky due to being teleported by [[Carol Danvers]]. Rambeau then became confident and used her abilities through her fights with [[Dar-Benn]]. Rambeau also grabbed Danvers from space while flying. Eventually, Rambeau had to be the one to fly out to a broken [[Universal Neural Teleportation Network|jump point]] and close it from the inside.
***'''Intangibility''': [[File:Monica absorbs bullets.png|thumb|250px|Rambeau phasing through bullets]] During the [[Battle of Westview]], Rambeau managed to phase through multiple gunshots inflicted on her by [[Tyler Hayward]] when the latter tried to kill [[Tommy Maximoff|Tommy]] and [[Billy Maximoff]], which caused her eyes to glow a golden yellow color. She also used this power during the skirmish between the [[Marvels]] and Kree warriors at the [[Khan Residence]] to phase through a rod a warrior had thrusted into her abdomen. While fighting [[Dar-Benn]], Rambeau utilized both her flight and intangibility to appear through the floor.
****'''Invisibility''': Rambeau turned invisible in order to sneak up on [[Dar-Benn]], which she can do through intangibility.

===Abilities===
<!-- The power list and levels has been carefully reviewed and approved with the media released post The Marvels. DO NOT MAKE arbitrary changes to them or it may lead to blocks. If something is wrong, please contact WikiProjects: Powers & Abilities -->
*'''Expert Combatant''': Rambeau is skilled in hand-to-hand combat, as she was able to take down multiple [[S.W.O.R.D.]] agents during her infiltration with [[Jimmy Woo]] and [[Darcy Lewis]]. She was also able to pin down [[Ralph Bohner]] before liberating him from [[Agatha Harkness]]' control. She was also skilled enough to contend with multiple [[Kree]] Soldiers and even fought [[Dar-Benn]] alongside [[Ms. Marvel|Kamala Khan]] and [[Captain Marvel]].
*'''Expert Marksman''': Rambeau is skilled in marksmanship, noted in her quick draw of [[Jimmy Woo]]'s handgun and rapid, accurate fire to the altered outfit that was manipulated from her kevlar vest after entering the [[Hex]]. She was also able to fire her energy beams with precision when she had her powers.
*'''Expert Investigator''': While under [[Wanda Maximoff]]'s spell, Rambeau was able to compromise Maximoff by talking about [[Pietro Maximoff]] and [[Ultron]]. This broke Maximoff's character and gave Rambeau a little information on what is happening in the Hex. [[Darcy Lewis]], [[Jimmy Woo]], and her were also able to figure out that [[Tyler Hayward]] was trying to get [[Vision/Chaos Magic Recreation|Vision]].

