===Other Equipment===
*'''Bulletproof Vest''': Rambeau wore a bulletproof vest when she first entered the [[Westview Anomaly]]. As she was brought into the Anomaly, [[Wanda Maximoff]]'s [[Magic#Chaos Magic|Chaos Magic]] transformed the vest into 1960s- and 1970s-era clothing as the era of the ''WandaVision'' sitcom that broadcasted [[Westview]]'s activities changed. When Rambeau was ejected from Westview, the bulletproof vest maintained its appearance as a 1970s-style outfit, even though it continued to be made out of Kevlar material.

===Vehicles===
*'''[[Humvee]]''': Rambeau used a Humvee to leave the [[S.W.O.R.D.]] [[S.W.O.R.D. Response Base|Response Base]] with [[Jimmy Woo]] after they were kicked off the base. When [[Wanda Maximoff]] [[Rescue of Vision|expanded]] the [[Westview Anomaly]], Rambeau and Woo used it to escape.
*'''[[S.W.O.R.D. Space Rover]]''': Rambeau asked [[Aly Goodner]] to put together a Space Rover for [[S.W.O.R.D.]], hoping to use it to reenter [[Westview]] with her memories in tact so she could talk to [[Wanda Maximoff]]. Rambeau attempted to use the Space Rover to enter Westview, but the [[Westview Anomaly]] still changed the nature of the Rover, forcing Rambeau to enter on her own.

